        <updateDate>2020-08-18T17:56:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Bonuses in Bankruptcy Act of 2019 </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits debtors in bankruptcy proceedings from paying bonuses to certain individuals, including insiders (such as relatives) and highly compensated employees. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
